DISP3D n

When DISP3D is set to 1, a graphic window is opened which will be 
used by the REF3D command to display 3D vues of the current3D data-
set. The size of the window is set to max(cx,cy,cz) in each 
dimension.

related contexts : $DISP3D

see also : DISP1D DISP2D CDISP2D REF3D CHECK3D DISP3D? PLOT3D ALPHA 
